#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 13. Nicchavitthisutta → nicchavitthi-aticārini (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Nicchavitthisutta "
msgstr "13. A Flayed Woman "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn19.13:1.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ nicchaviṃ itthiṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantiṃ. "
msgstr "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a flayed woman flying through the air. "

msgctxt "sn19.13:1.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā vitacchenti virājenti. "
msgstr "Vultures, crows, and hawks kept chasing her, pecking, plucking, and hacking "

msgctxt "sn19.13:1.3"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … "
msgstr "as she screamed in pain. …” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.13:1.4"
msgid "esā, bhikkhave, itthī imasmiṃyeva rājagahe aticārinī ahosi … pe …. "
msgstr "“That woman used to be an adulteress right here in Rājagaha. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.13:1.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

